OL,3,CSix-time Olympic champion Sir Chris
OL,4,CHoy reveals his cancer is terminal
OL,6,FSir Chris Hoy, one of Britain's
OL,7,Fgreatest cyclists and Olympians, has
OL,8,Frevealed that his cancer diagnosis is
OL,9,Fterminal.
OL,11,FIn an interview with The Sunday Times,
OL,12,Fthe former Team GB track cyclist says
OL,13,Fhe has been given a diagnosis and has
OL,14,Ftwo to four years left to live.
OL,16,F"As unnatural as it feels, this is
OL,17,Fnature."
OL,19,FHe added: "You know, we were all born
OL,20,Fand we all die, and this is just part
OL,21,Fof the process.
