OL,3,CSix-time Olympic champion Sir Chris
OL,4,CHoy reveals his cancer is terminal
OL,6,F"You remind yourself, aren't I lucky
OL,7,Fthat there is medicine I can take that
OL,8,Fwill fend this off for as long as
OL,9,Fpossible."
OL,11,FHoy announced in February that he was
OL,12,Fundergoing treatment for cancer,
OL,13,Fincluding chemotherapy, following his
OL,14,Fdiagnosis last year.
OL,16,FThe 48-year-old, who has two children
OL,17,Faged seven and ten, said at the time
OL,18,Fthat he was "optimistic" and his
OL,19,Ftreatment was going "really well".
