OL,3,CSix-time Olympic champion Sir Chris
OL,4,CHoy reveals his cancer is terminal
OL,6,FIn a new interview, he said a tumour
OL,7,Fwas found in his shoulder last
OL,8,FSeptember, and a second scan found the
OL,9,Fprimary cancer in his prostate, which
OL,10,Fhad metastasised to his bones. He has
OL,11,Ftumours in his shoulder, pelvis, hip,
OL,12,Fspine and rib.
OL,14,FThis story is being updated, more
OL,15,Ffollows
